snippet.title: ANIMALS that will make you LAUGH ALL DAY, EVERY DAY! - The FUNNIEST VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Very funny animal & pet videos. Try not to laugh all you want but you will fail, this is simply too funny! Bet you will laugh so super hard that you will fall out of your chair! Just look how all these kittens, cats, puppies, dogs, sheep, mini pigs, squirrel, parrot, baby ducks,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
